Package: histopathR
Type: Package
Title: Template and R Codes Used in Histopathologic Research 
Version: 0.0.0.9001
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Serdar",
           family = "Balci",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "drserdarbalci@gmail.com",
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-7852-3851"))
Maintainer: Serdar Balci <drserdarbalci@gmail.com>
Description: This package is a collection of R codes that I use in my research.
    I have added clinicopathological analysis templates.
    I plan to add bibliometrics, image analysis and text analysis templates as well.
    It will include how to prepare data for statistical analysis.
    Methods to import and prepare data for analysis.
    Descriptive statistics.
    Hypothesis tests.
    Survival analysis.
    Regression analysis.
    Cluster analysis.
